notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:09.573Z",codex-root,Specialized pm plan create does not expose every strict-required Plan field; create the Plan via pm create and manage steps via pm plan.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:09.573Z",codex-root,"Under strict PM governance,use the generic create surface for fully specified Plan items when the specialized constructor lacks policy-required fields."
