plan_decisions[2]{ts,author,decision,rationale,evidence}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:58.523Z",codex-root,Upgrade direct dependencies and action majors as one coherent compatibility bundle.,Fifteen overlapping bot branches are stale against the same lockfile and cannot independently reach test execution.,PR 51 run 26775340556 and PR 50 run 26673365486 both fail bun install --frozen-lockfile.
  "2026-07-16T17:01:15.418Z",codex-root,Keep TypeScript on 5.9 and Node typings on 22 while adopting other current majors.,typescript-eslint 8.64 requires TypeScript below 6.1; the package supports Node 22.19 and should type against its actual runtime line.,npm registry peerDependencies and engines inspected on 2026-07-16; lint/typecheck/build passed after compatible pins.
plan_discoveries[2]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:54:56.876Z",codex-root,All representative Dependabot CI failures occur before tests because bun.lock is not regenerated with package.json.
  "2026-07-16T16:54:57.745Z",codex-root,"Local bun audit finds 28 advisories, broader than the single GitHub alert, including vulnerable runtime Undici, ws, and YAML paths."
